  "excerpt": "<p>On the tenth day of Christmas, Katie Crafts gave to me… Not one, not two, but THREE amazing gift guides for you to shop! All three of these boards that are chock full of Christmas gift ideas are courtesy of Anna from Gentle Decisions. Aren’t they lovely!? Check out each of the treasuries below and shop your little Christmas hearts out!</p>\n",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>?On the tenth day of Christmas, Katie Crafts gave to me…?</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Not one, not two, but THREE amazing gift guides for you to shop! All three of these boards that are chock full of Christmas gift ideas are courtesy of <em><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/GentleDecisions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Anna from Gentle Decisions</a></em>. Aren’t they lovely!? Check out each of the treasuries below and shop your little Christmas hearts out!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Before you get to shopping, <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/GentleDecisions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">check out Anna’s shop</a>! It’s filled with beautiful hand crafted floral accessories that you will totally love. Also feel free to check out the original treasuries <strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTc4MjI0MDZ8MjcyODA1Nzk1MA/christmas-gift-ideas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here,</a> <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTc4MjI0MDZ8MjcyODA1NzkyNA/christmas-gift-ideas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a> <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTc4MjI0MDZ8MjcyNTQ5NTQ3Mw/christmas-gift-ideas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">and here!</a></strong> Now, on to shopping!! Enjoy!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">\n<ol>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/168254101/joy-to-the-world-modern-christmas?ref=tre-2728057950-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Richwood Creations</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/207365023/coffee-shade-matt-silk-wedding-gown-with?ref=tre-2728057950-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cathy Telle</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/161355725/diy-putz-church-ornament-kit-christmas?ref=tre-2728057950-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Holiday Spirits Decor</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/212576145/prettylover-statement-white-colors-jade?ref=tre-2728057950-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Pardes</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/219808789/free-shipping-set-of-2-white-linen?ref=tre-2728057950-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Not Perfect Linen</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/113890500/christmas-tree-snow-white-christmis?ref=tre-2728057950-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fairy Folk</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/182570984/shaded-landscape-wall-mural-wallpaper?ref=tre-2728057950-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Anewall</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/254224702/new-glass-geometric-candle-holder?ref=tre-2728057950-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Waen</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/219318552/winter-wonderland-bear-soft-sculpture?ref=tre-2728057950-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Past Your Porchlight</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/227703502/chrome-set-of-3-succulents-in-hexagonal?ref=tre-2728057950-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Waterstone Succulents</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/248593805/knit-infinity-scarf-chunky-ribbed-marble?ref=tre-2728057950-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Debrosse NYC</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/113686407/papyrus-origami-christmas-tree-topper?ref=tre-2728057950-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Goraygami</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/lis